data.text/markdown:
UK Crime Data Analysis

Configuration

This notebook implements a bisection strategy to download UK crime data from the Police API. API Constraints:
  • Max 10,000 crimes per request (returns 403 if exceeded)
  • Max 10 calls per second
  • Target: 5,000-7,500 crimes per area

data.text/html:
Execution Controls

Test the bisection algorithm on a small area before running on the entire UK.

Ready to Execute

Date: 2024-01 Area: Large Test (All England) Click the button below to start the bisection algorithm.
